      "widgets_values": [
        "=== 02-face-portrait — RETRATO DE ROSTRO CENTRADO ===\n\nWorkflow basado en 01-base-sprite.json\nPurpose: Bust shot/close-up para que el rostro sea\nel elemento central. Ideal para variantes de expresión.\n\n=== CAMBIOS RESPECTO A 01-base-sprite ===\n\nBase:  832x1040 (ratio 4:5, encuadre bust/rostro)\nHires: 1248x1560 (Remacri 4x → resize lanczos)\nPrompt+ : bust shot, close-up portrait, face focus,\n          looking at viewer — SIN cowboy shot\nPrompt- : añade waist down, legs, hands, back angle\nSaveImage: dnd3_face\n\n=== RECURSOS (mismos que 01-base-sprite) ===\n\nCHECKPOINT → ComfyUI/models/checkpoints/\n  perfectDeliberate_v8.safetensors\n\nLoRAs → ComfyUI/models/loras/\n  748cmSDXL.safetensors          strength: 0.5\n  thiccwithaq-artist-richy-v1_ixl.safetensors  strength: 0.7\n  USNR_STYLE_ILL_V1_lokr3-000024.safetensors   strength: 0.6\n\nUPSCALER → ComfyUI/models/upscale_models/\n  4x_remacri.pth\n\n=== SETTINGS ===\nSteps base: 38  |  Steps hires: 20\nCFG: 4  |  Denoise hires: 0.55\nSampler: DPM++ 2M Karras  |  CLIP skip: -2\nSeed: 1088048497 (fixed — cambiar para variar)\n\n⚠ Testear manualmente antes de integrar al generador.\n  Ajustar prompt de expresión neutral si es necesario."
